{"tid":565209,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【生葬11日】巴女額頭敲棺求救 掘起屍體仲暖但已太遲","createTime":"2018-02-18T17:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T00:33:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8b358f810fa819b9cd510fbd961c5738577f657b","tid":565209,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:55:55.000Z","msg":"巴西一名因病出現休克的女子疑被醫院誤判死亡，放入棺木後再安葬。直至11天後有民眾聽到她敲棺求救，但可惜掘起開棺為時已晚，女子送院後證實死亡，而且屍體仍有餘溫，或證明只是死去不久。<br />\n<br />\n37歲的桑托斯（Rosangela Almeida dos Santos）上月中因過勞症入院留醫一周，後來心臟病發兼出現感染性休克（septic shock），在同月28日被院方「證實死亡」，並於翌日入棺下葬。<br />\n<br />\n然而途人席爾瓦（Natalina Silva）本月9日行經桑托斯下葬的墳場附近時，隱約聽到傳來敲撞聲及低呻聲，「當我走到（桑托斯）墓碑前，我聽到有些撞擊聲，我起初以為是孩童們的惡作劇。然後我聽到她低呻2聲，在那之後就停止了。」<br />\n<br />\n席爾瓦向有關方面反映後，桑托斯的家人決定起棺查明真相，稱驚見桑托斯的額頭及手出現傷痕，棺木內有刮痕及血迹，釘緊棺木板的鐵釘亦稍稍變形，意味她曾在棺內激烈掙扎。<br />\n<br />\n家人相信桑托斯當初是被誤判死亡，她的姊妹說：「我們不是想指摘任何醫生，也不想惹來麻煩，但我們親眼看到了，一個人沒可能在下葬11天後屍身仍暖。」警方已接手調查，涉嫌誤判她死亡的醫院透過代表稱，院方會提供一切所需的資料協助。<br />\n<br />\n英國《都市報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/015450_973de16e3713d99c8a6d55cd877e1a03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F015450_973de16e3713d99c8a6d55cd877e1a03.png&h=2cb96ace&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/015452_76f5fc9693d5c71b84d4909fe9adce8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F015452_76f5fc9693d5c71b84d4909fe9adce8a.png&h=7708db37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180218/57844117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57844117&d=yy7YXDl9ly5dWYWlFrbr4KS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=705ade73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57844117&h=3a0df94d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180218/57844117</a><br />\n<br />\nRip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbf341fdc78c91c3491f95de26af1ec940a238e","tid":565209,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"真係絕望到極點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0943e1e90533f6936f9404b865b2969960f37bdb","tid":565209,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:02:12.000Z","msg":"面對死亡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果種絕望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3174e91c55d837500c293502bed5de2705950d6","tid":565209,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f118a5e6e25be77e2bcfccc0b4798abd897ae20d","tid":565209,"uid":59789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:09:07.000Z","msg":"&quot;28日被院方「證實死亡」，並於翌日入棺下葬&quot;<br />\n外國人做野真係快, 香港起碼要一個星期"},{"pid":"488df1327e37782d4e716405ea42eb4df9640ae5","tid":565209,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f118a5e6e25be77e2bcfccc0b4798abd897ae20d","tid":565209,"uid":59789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:09:07.000Z","msg":"&quot;28日被院方「證實死亡」，並於翌日入棺下葬&quot;<br />\n外國人做野真係快, 香港起碼要一個星期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"支那都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f4aed6162968e47a0ae73604d31a9d9f60511a","tid":565209,"uid":17103,"li